properties.name: Rowland Street
properties.description: Named for Percy Fritz Rowland, headmaster of Townsville Grammar, 1905-1938 (Mathew, 2008, p. 109).
properties.refs: Mathew, J. (2008). Highways and Byways: The Origin of Townsville Street Names (Revised ed.). Townsville, QLD: Townsville Library Service.

properties.name: Marshall Street
properties.description: Named for Alfred Marshall, local surveyor in Townsville during the 1880s (Mathew, 2008, p. 84).
properties.refs: Mathew, J. (2008). Highways and Byways: The Origin of Townsville Street Names (Revised ed.). Townsville, QLD: Townsville Library Service.
